data.description: Totally move-in ready! There is a new kitchen with beautiful white shaker door cabinetry, side-by-side pantry cabinets, butcher block counters, and a new dishwasher. Includes all appl. New Mini-Split Ductless heat and air. Vinyl windows, new blinds in the living room. Primary BR offers a large walk-in closet. Home has 2 lots for a half an acre lot. There is a huge fenced yard, garden spaces, a large 2 car garage with a recent new roof, plus extra parking for boat and RV. Located in a charming Eastside neighborhood at the end of a dead-end street. Close to St. Michaels, State buildings, & downtown. Includes a dog pen too.   Check with the city to see what you could do with the extra lot, Buyer to verify the lot size and SF.
